<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
前陣子非常謝謝你<delay20 />
把你的自創詩集送給我喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喔～不會啦，<delay20 />那你覺得如何？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有沒有發現喜歡的詩啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是有一首詩
把我比喻成<delay20 />
<tag a="135" b="2" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的非常浪漫，<delay8 />
我很喜歡喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />因為它惹人憐愛這點
真的跟你一個樣啊！<delay20 />哈哈──！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />我發現
裡面有幾個錯字，<delay20 />
所以我修正過後，<delay8 />寄回去給你了喔。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喔喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />
我覺得你認真的一面<delay8 />也很棒喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是<delay20 />有一首詩
把我比喻成甜～蜜蜜的<delay8 />
<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我覺得有點害羞呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />因為甜蜜蜜這點
真的跟你一個樣啊！<delay20 />哈哈──！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />我發現
裡面有幾個錯字，<delay20 />
所以我修正過後，<delay8 />寄回去給你了喔。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喔喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
看來甜蜜中帶有一點苦味呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />我覺得
你這一面<delay8 />也很棒喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是有一首詩
把我比喻成<colour id="1" />機場<colour id="65535" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人很意外，<delay8 />我覺得很不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為飛機場可以讓<delay20 />
翱翔在空中的飛機休息嘛。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你就是那種<delay8 />
讓人感到安心的存在啊！<delay frames="30" />哈哈──！</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />我發現
裡面有幾個錯字，<delay20 />
所以我修正過後，<delay8 />寄回去給你了喔。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喔喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
看來這座<colour id="1" />機場<colour id="65535" />的檢查<delay8 />
相當嚴格呢。
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，我覺得<delay20 />這種不輕易放行的一面<delay20 />
正是你的魅力喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 04 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />話說我剛剛<delay20 />
正好在問<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
一天會照幾次鏡子呢。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />順便問一下，<delay8 />那<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你一天會照幾次呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">兩、三次左右</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一天到晚都在照</message>
	<message label="101_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">完全不照</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀哎呀，<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />
要是不多照幾次，<delay8 />
感覺鏡子很可憐啊。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我啊，<delay8 />
就整天都在照鏡子喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為不管怎麼樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得鏡子<delay8 />一定也很想看我！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇！<delay frames="40" />
原來你不是要用鏡子看自己，<delay8 />
而是反過來，想讓鏡子看你啊！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟我想讓鏡子看看<delay20 />
最完美的我嘛！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你們要不要<delay20 />也讓鏡子<delay8 />
看看最完美的自己啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="7" />這麼一想，<delay20 />
我就覺得<delay8 />有點不好意思照鏡子了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
你能大大方方地面對鏡子，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我覺得好厲害喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />我也跟你一樣！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺我跟你應該有某種命運牽引呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得只要看到鏡子裡的自己，<delay20 />
心情就會莫名平靜嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我都會<delay20 />看著鏡子<delay20 />
來療癒自己的心靈啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />的確是呢！<20_2 arg="1" /><delay20 />生氣的時候，
只要一看到鏡中的自己，<delay20 />
感覺就會冷靜下來。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
你說的話<delay8 /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />果然不同凡響呢。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是啊，<delay20 />只要全世界的鏡子
都映照出我的模樣，<delay20 />
大家乾涸的心靈就能獲得療癒了說<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說要怎麼做<delay8 />
才能讓所有鏡子<delay8 />都映照出
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的樣子呢<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒關係……<delay8 />這點就之後再來研究吧。<delay20 />
我想我也來嘗試<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多照幾遍鏡子好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="2" />居然有這種事！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果鏡子不照你，<delay20 />
它還有其他東西好照嗎！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="7" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
我覺得你這樣……<delay20 />
自然又不做作，很棒喔！
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哪像我，<delay20 />吃完東西後，
都會很在意嘴巴周圍有沒有污漬，<delay20 />
老是會<delay8 />忍不住看起鏡子呢。</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_3 arg="4" /><20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />手邊沒有鏡子的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就把我當成鏡子，<delay20 />
看看我眼裡映照出的你吧，如何？
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來吧，<delay frames="40" />看著我的眼睛<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
靠近點，<delay20 />再靠近點<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇，<delay20 />好像很浪漫呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />要是一直對看的話，
眼睛就會變得乾乾的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />記得要適時地眨一下眼喔。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay8 />真的好巧喔！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
沒想到你也在讀一樣的書！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想這不是巧合，<delay20 />
而是命運的牽引喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了！<delay frames="40" />既然都這麼巧了，
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如我也把口頭禪
改成和你一樣好了！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你常說的那個<delay8 />「<tag a="110" b="5" />」，<delay20 />
也讓我用用看吧！</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是可以啦<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" />「<tag a="110" b="6" />」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
「<tag a="110" b="6" />」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的「<tag a="110" b="5" />」！<delay frames="30" />聽起來怎麼樣？
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經離不開<delay20 />
這個口頭禪啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個嘛<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />我覺得還不錯喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
